============================================================
PHASE 9 OBJECTIVE
============================================================

Build the enterprise cloud scale layer for zDash.

Main goals:

1. Add multi-tenant SaaS architecture
2. Add organizations and workspaces
3. Add tenant-scoped RBAC
4. Add queue worker system
5. Add Redis-backed background jobs
6. Add WebSocket live event stream
7. Add alerting and notification system
8. Add Cloudflare deployment support
9. Add Terraform infrastructure templates
10. Add Kubernetes deployment manifests
11. Add release automation scripts
12. Add system runbooks
13. Add frontend organization/workspace UI
14. Add tenant-aware dashboard data isolation
15. Add enterprise-grade tests

IMPORTANT SAFETY RULES:
- Do not enable live trading by default.
- Do not enable real IoT actions by default.
- Do not enable real social posting by default.
- Do not bypass Guardian risk checks.
- Do not bypass content approval checks.
- Tenant isolation is mandatory.
- A user from one tenant must never access another tenant’s data.
- All external cloud integrations must be dry-run or template-first by default.
- Never hardcode Cloudflare tokens, cloud credentials, SSH keys, broker credentials, API keys, or secrets.
- All deploy scripts must fail safely.

